trans-unit.target: Fornece dados para o evento de <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError" /> .

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError> event is raised when an attempt to create a new user with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control fails.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError> evento é gerado quando uma tentativa de criar um novo usuário com o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> controlar falhar.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs> class provides the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs.CreateUserError%2A> property to indicate the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipCreateStatus> enumeration value that corresponds to the error that occurred.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs> classe fornece a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs.CreateUserError%2A> propriedade para indicar o <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipCreateStatus> valor de enumeração que corresponde ao erro que ocorreu.

trans-unit.source: In the following example, when the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError> event is raised, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs.CreateUserError%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs> object is displayed in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label> control, `Label1`, to provide information on why the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError> event occurred.
trans-unit.target: No exemplo a seguir, quando o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError> é gerado, o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs.CreateUserError%2A> propriedade o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserErrorEventArgs> objeto é exibido em um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label> controle, `Label1`, para fornecer informações sobre por que o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard.CreateUserError> evento ocorreu.
